Title: Camera with privacy protection
Technical data: Camera with extra privacy
Rich Text: Affordable, easy to use camera for surveillance in alarm cases. Camera has HW connected buzzer and led to guaranty warning to user when camera is in use. Camera use low resolution video protect privacy and reduce bandwidth. It also adjust frames per second based on communication link.

Title: Ear Thermometer
